'''Ijider awraɣ''' ([[Assaɣ usnan]]: ''Aquila chrysaetos'') d [[tisekliwin|asekliw]] yettwassenen yakk deg wezgen n umadal agafaw, akken iga daɣen d [[talmest]] meqqren yakk deg [[ijider|ijudar]], yeṭṭafar [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[iberniyen]] am telmas n iden deg [[tawsit (tudersent)|tewsit-is]], Zik nni yella yezdeɣ yakk deg yidgan n ugafa n [[tagnit|tegnit]] maca tura [[angar|inger]] deg waṭas n yidgan igra-d kan deg [[iger|igran]] d [[tagant|tẓegwa]] yaggugen (ibeɛden) ɣef yidgan ittwazdaɣen d [[afgan|ifganen]] ɣas yella-d wannecg-a maca mazal-it yettidir deg waṭas n yidgan seg [[Asya]] ar [[Turuft|Uruppa]] d [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] d [[Tamrikt n Ugafa]] aladɣa di [[Kalifurnya]] 

== [[Tagemra|Agmar]] ==
Ijider awraɣ igemmer s ugani ɣef [[Akacbar|ikacbaren-is]] imesden d tazla-ynes yeflalen, Umuɣ n tgemrawin-is meqqer acku dges [[awtul|iwtal]], [[Yuzaṭ]], [[Anẓid|inẓiden]] ula d [[abareɣ|iburaɣ]] akk d [[Amcic|yemcac]]

== [[Amyaraw]] ==
Ijider awraɣ d [[aɣersiw]] ayentyuga, ixeddem-d yiwen n unarag (acrik) kan deg teɣzi n tudert-is, yal tayuga tettaṭaf tajumma yettawaṭen ar 155 km anda iy ferren ideg yeflalen i tmuska (lebni) n [[agdef|ugdef]] i wakken ad issers dges [[tamellalt|timellalin-is]], Deg yal tikkelt ssrusayen yiwet n tmellalt neɣ kuẓ (4) 

== Aglam ==
Ijider awraɣ d [[tisekliwin|aselkiw]] yuddsen s waṭas, [[afraw|afraw-is]] d aras, [[afriw|Afriwen-is]] hraw-it, Teɣzi ynes tettili gar n  70 ar 85 cm ma d afriwen-is seg yiri ar yiri mara ad ldin ttilin seg 185 ar 220 cm, [[azuk|Azuk-is]] yettili gar n 3,8 ar 6,7 kg i [[Tawtemt|tewtemt]] yugaren [[awtem]] (seg 2,8 ar 4,6 kg i [[Awtem|wewtem]])

== Asismel ==
[[Tasnaɣersiwt|Amusnaw n iɣersiwen]] n [[Swid]] [[Carl con Linné]] igelm-d iylalen-a s tugna tusnant i tikkelt tamenzut deg uskar-is ''[[anagraw agaman]]'' deg useggas n [[1758]] dgi is-yefka isem n [[tawsit (tudersent)|tewsit]] ''Falco'' anda iy ɣil de akken-it n [[aseflay|iseflayen]], send ma ad s-yales (ad s-iɛawed) umusnaw [[Fransa|afṛensis]] ([[Mathurin Jacques Brisson]]) [[tasartut n tesnudert|asismel]] w ad s-yefk isem n tewsit ''Aquila'' deg useggas n 1760

